      <!--       anything. If it works, great!  If it doesn<rsq/>t, don't do -->
      <!--       something incorrectly to try and force it. Try something -->
      <!--       else. Our Rule of Thumb will help, but there are no guarantees. This is -->
      <!--       what makes integration harder than differentiation, much as -->
